    "name": "Forestrike — 预视武宗",
    "steam_appid": 2325920,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Forestrike — 预视武宗》是一款武术类轻度肉鸽游戏，灵感来自于经典武打电影，每场战斗都是独一无二的，每一次死亡都会让你离胜利更近一步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将扮演武术家阿聿在国内四处奔走，设法解救落入邪恶将领手中的君主。形势变得越来越不利，为了战胜邪恶将领的恶毒爪牙，阿聿需要超越双拳之外的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“推演”是一种神秘的能力，能让阿聿在自己的脑海中构建出要塞中的每一场遭遇战。在战斗开始前掌握战斗局势，虽然不一定能保证在现实中获胜，但可以为阿聿争取胜算。每一步行动都至关重要，因为死亡是有代价的——再次踏上旅程，从头再来一遍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿聿虽然可以取得胜利，但也不能毫发无损地从每一次遭遇中脱身，因此需要精心规划才能顺利穿越每一张随机生成的世界地图。你可以利用客栈来休息，也可以向沿途遇到的睿智大师讨教。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿聿越是深入探索，就会变得越强大，最终会从五位异乎寻常的大师那里学到新的技能，带来永久升级。将这些技能组合起来，尝试新的可能性，实现阿聿的终极目标——无需“推演之力”就能取得胜利。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >洞察先机，有备而来</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Forestrike — 预视武宗》采用独特的预见机制，玩家可在实战前尽情演练各种进攻方式，直到最终取胜。游戏采用 Roguelike 游戏循环，每场游戏与战斗都不一样，因此临机应变就是推动进度的关键，最后也要依靠临机应变达成终极胜利，而不是推演之力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325920/extras/121a1d9b8bef6b3f38189ee17269d728.poster.avif?t=1763823448\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325920/extras/121a1d9b8bef6b3f38189ee17269d728.webm?t=1763823448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325920/extras/121a1d9b8bef6b3f38189ee17269d728.mp4?t=1763823448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >顺应本能的功夫战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以少战多，学习如何镇定高效地击退大批强敌，同时善用手头的物品。面对谜题般的激烈战斗时，运用所选宗师传授的技巧，精进和搭配招式组合，智取对手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325920/extras/394ce9bd16302fb6d7fba8506210915e.poster.avif?t=1763823448\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325920/extras/394ce9bd16302fb6d7fba8506210915e.webm?t=1763823448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325920/extras/394ce9bd16302fb6d7fba8506210915e.mp4?t=1763823448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >手工制作的奇幻世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入令人目不转睛的奇幻世界，领略独特角色、凶狠敌人和魔幻启发。而精细的像素风景观构建了一个沉浸感十足的舞台，与手工制作的动画和角色相得益彰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325920/extras/4c0ae6660ba8ab200dde724887984cfd.poster.avif?t=1763823448\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325920/extras/4c0ae6660ba8ab200dde724887984cfd.webm?t=1763823448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325920/extras/4c0ae6660ba8ab200dde724887984cfd.mp4?t=1763823448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
